dend

Class Graph

  • java.lang.Object
    • dend.Graph

  • public class Graph
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents an undirected graph to allow visiting the skeleton in an efficient way. Modified based on Graph.java of the ImageJ AnalyzeSkeleton_ plugin by Ignacio Arganda-Carreras.

    For more information about the original plugin, visit the AnalyzeSkeleton home page: http://fiji.sc/AnalyzeSkeleton

    Author:
    Diana Bank, Elena Zhong, Chun Han Lab, Cornell University
